<html><body><p>Last June, <a title="FVRG Website" href="http://www.fvrg.co.uk/" target="_blank">Fierce Valley Roller Girls</a> embraced all things Grease-related in their first intraleague bout, <a title="SRD Advert for Summer Shovin'" href="http://scottishrollerderbyblog.com/2012/06/18/fvrg-intra-league-summer-shovin/" target="_blank">Summer Shovin'</a>.

