The FVRG bout will be held in Grangemouth Sports Complex. Tickets are charged at Â£5 in advance, and under 14s go free with a paying adult. Due to the limited seating at this venue, tickets will be sold on a first-come, first-served basis - and from <a title="http://revengeofthefallen.brownpapertickets.com/" href="But%20Tickets%20Online" target="_blank">Brown Paper Tickets</a> only.

